nterop\": true,\n    \"skipLibCheck\": true,\n    \"forceConsistentCasingInFileNames\": true,\n    \"resolveJsonModule\": true,\n    \"declaration\": true,\n    \"declarationMap\": true,\n    \"sourceMap\": true\n  },\n  \"include\": [\"src/**/*\"],\n  \"exclude\": [\"node_modules\", \"dist\", \"tests\"]\n}\n```\n\n#### **.eslintrc.cjs**\n```javascript\nmodule.exports = {\n  parser: '@typescript-eslint/parser',\n  plugins: ['@typescript-eslint'],\n  extends: ['eslint:recommended', 'plugin:@typescript-eslint/recommended'],\n  parserOptions: {\n    ecmaVersion: 2022,\n    sourceType: 'module',\n  },\n  rules: {\n    '@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars': ['error', { argsIgnorePattern: '^_', varsIgnorePattern: '^_' }],\n  },\n  env: {\n    node: true,\n    es2022: true,\n  },\n};\n```\n\n#### **vitest.config.ts**\n```typescript\nimport { defineConfig } from 'vitest/config';\n\nexport default defineConfig({\n  test: {\n    globals: true,\n    testTimeout: 10000,\n  },\n});\n```\n\n#### **.gitignore**\n```\nnode_modules/\ndist/\n*.tsbuildinfo\n```\n\n### Project Task Summary (from TASK.md)\nThe task requires building a `Spreadsheet` class with the following features:\n\n**Required API Methods:**\n- `set(cell: string, value: string | number | boolean)` — Set a cell's value or formula\n- `get(cell: string)` — Get a cell's computed value (returns null for empty cells)\n- `getDisplay(cell: string)` — Get the display string for a cell's computed value\n- `getCells()` — Get all non-empty cells as a Map\n\n**Supported Cell Types:**\n- Numbers, strings, booleans, and formulas (starting with `=`)\n\n**Supported Operators:**\n- Arithmetic: `+`, `-`, `*`, `/`\n- Comparison: `>`, `<`, `>=`, `<=`, `=`, `<>`\n- Parentheses for grouping\n\n**Built-in Functions:**\n- `SUM(range)`, `AVERAGE(range)`, `MIN(range)`, `MAX(range)`, `COUNT(range)`, `IF(condition, trueValue, falseValue)`\n\n**Special Features:**\n- **Ranges:** `A1:A5`, `A1:C1`, `A1:C3` (column, row, and block ranges)\n- **Reactiv