n              # TypeScript configuration\n├── vitest.config.ts           # Vitest test runner configuration\n└── src/                       # Source directory (only .gitkeep currently)\n```\n\n### Key Configuration Files\n\n#### **package.json**\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"bench-reactive-spreadsheet\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"description\": \"Reactive spreadsheet engine benchmark\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"tsc\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint src/\",\n    \"test\": \"vitest run\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@types/node\": \"^22.0.0\",\n    \"@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin\": \"^7.0.0\",\n    \"@typescript-eslint/parser\": \"^7.0.0\",\n    \"@vitest/coverage-v8\": \"^2.0.0\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^8.56.0\",\n    \"tsx\": \"^4.0.0\",\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.4.0\",\n    \"vitest\": \"^2.0.0\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n#### **tsconfig.json**\n```json\n{\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    \"target\": \"ES2022\",\n    \"module\": \"Node16\",\n    \"moduleResolution\": \"Node16\",\n    \"outDir\": \"./dist\",\n    \"rootDir\": \"./src\",\n    \"strict\": true,\n    \"esModuleInterop\": true,\n    \"skipLibCheck\": true,\n    \"forceConsistentCasingInFileNames\": true,\n    \"resolveJsonModule\": true,\n    \"declaration\": true,\n    \"declarationMap\": true,\n    \"sourceMap\": true\n  },\n  \"include\": [\"src/**/*\"],\n  \"exclude\": [\"node_modules\", \"dist\", \"tests\"]\n}\n```\n\n#### **.eslintrc.cjs**\n```javascript\nmodule.exports = {\n  parser: '@typescript-eslint/parser',\n  plugins: ['@typescript-eslint'],\n  extends: ['eslint:recommended', 'plugin:@typescript-eslint/recommended'],\n  parserOptions: {\n    ecmaVersion: 2022,\n    sourceType: 'module',\n  },\n  rules: {\n    '@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars': ['error', { argsIgnorePattern: '^_', varsIgnorePattern: '^_' }],\n  },\n  env: {\n    node: true,\n    es2022: true,\n  },\n};\n```\n\n#### **vitest.config.ts**\n```typescript\nimport { defineConfig } from 'vitest/config';\n\nexport default defineConfig({\n  test: {\n    globals: true,\n    testTimeout: 10000,\n  },\n});\n```\n\n#### **.gitignore**\n```\nnode_modules/\ndist/\n*.tsbuildinfo\n```\n\n### Project Task Summary (from TASK.md)\nThe task requires building a `Spreadsheet` class with the following features:\n\n**Required API Methods:**\n- `set(cell: string, value: string | number | boolean)` — Set a cell's value or formula\n- `get(cell: string)` — Get a cell's computed value (returns null for empty cells)\n- `getDisplay(cell: string)` — Get the display string for a cell's computed value\n- `getCells()` — Get all non-empty cells as a Map\n\n**Supported Cell Types:**\n- Numbers, strings, booleans, and formulas (starting with `=`)\n\n**Supported Operators:**\n- Arithmetic: `+`, `-`, `*`, `/`\n- Comparison: `>`, `<`, `>=`, `<=`, `=`, `<>`\n- Parentheses for grouping\n\n**Built-in Functions:**\n- `SUM(range)`, `AVERAGE(range)`, `MIN(range)`, `MAX(range)`, `COUNT(range)`, `IF(condition, trueValue, falseValue)`\n\n**Special Features:**\n- **Ranges:** `A1:A5`, `A1:C1`, `A1:C3` (column, row, and block ranges)\n- **Reactive Updates:** Automatic recomputation of dependent cells\n- **Circular Reference Detection:** Must throw error for circular dependencies\n\n### Build & Development Scripts\n- `npm run build` — TypeScript compilation to `/dist`\n- `npm run lint` — ESLint code quality checks\n- `npm run test` — Run tests with Vitest\n\n### Current State\n- **src/ directory:** Empty (only `.gitkeep` file exists) - ready for implementation\n- **TypeScript:** Strict mode enabled with full type checking\n- **Testing:** Vitest configured with 10-second timeout per test\n- **Output:** TypeScript compiles to `/dist` with source maps and declaration files"}],"totalDurationMs":14425,"totalTokens":15598,"totalToolUseCount":10,"usage":{"input_tokens":7,"cache_creation_input_tokens":344,"cache_read_input_tokens":13911,"output_tokens":1336,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_req